                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was on the Key, and saw the prisoner take it away, and informed the last witness of it.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>If I did it I know nothing about it; I don't know that I did.</p>
